com.interpss.core.algo
Interface CustomLFMethod

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
All Known Implementing Classes:
CustomLFMethodImpl
public interface CustomLFMethod
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject

A representation of the model object 'Custom LF Method'. Custom LF method will allow user to define two LF mathods, for example, PQ first and then NR. The switching could be at the 5th iteration or when error less than 0.001pu

The following features are supported:

  • First Method
  • Second Method
  • Switch Criteria
  • Switch Iteration
  • Switch Tolerance

See Also:
CoreAlgorithmPackage.getCustomLFMethod()
